OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThe $5m 'Prove Mike Wrong' 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fchallenge that backfired   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The founder of US bedding company My   
OL,6, Pillow has been ordered to pay $5m     
OL,7, (#4m) to an expert who proved his 2020 
OL,8, presidential election data was wrong.  
OL,10,FElection denier Mike Lindell was so    
OL,11,Fsure he had data showing Chinese       
OL,12,Finterference in the 2020 vote that he  
OL,13,Fthrew down the gauntlet to others.     
OL,15,FIn 2021 he launched "Prove Mike Wrong" 
OL,16,Fwith $5m as a winning prize.           
OL,18,FOn Wednesday, a private arbitration    
OL,19,Fpanel ruled that a software expert did 
OL,20,Fexactly that and was due the money.    
